title: Nouman Ali Khan Selected Lectures
description:
Selected lectures by Nouman Ali Khan

Nouman Ali Khan is an American Muslim speaker of Pakistani origin. He is the founder, CEO and lead instructor at The Bayyinah Institute for Arabic and Qur'anic Studies. The fifth edition of The 500 Most Influential Muslims listed him as one of the most influential Muslims in the world without any specific ranking.
